    "description": "Are you a skilled E-commerce Executive looking for your next big career move? Tata CLiQ Capital India in Pune offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Tata CLiQ Capital India:\nTata CLiQ Capital India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata CLiQ Capital India!",
